[Student "S"]
{SOUTH opens 2\C with her balanced 25 points.

NORTH has 9 points but no 5-card suit. He should make a positive response of 2NT.

SOUTH figures NORTH for 8 points and bids 6NT. If NORTH has significantly more than 
8 it will be up to him to go to 7NT. But he doesn't.}

